This paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as it focuses on learning optimal feedback control laws for robotic applications. The use of deep learning techniques also suggests that it could belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category. The paper also deals with control systems, which could place it in the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category. The use of reinforcement learning and optimal control methods suggests that it could also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Finally, the use of deep differential networks and the focus on learning value functions suggests that it could belong to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
